<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Your Daily Quote</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #111827, #1f2937, #111827);
            color: #ffffff;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: rgba(31, 41, 55, 0.8); /* gray-800 with opacity */
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
            border: 1px solid #374151; /* gray-700 */
            border-radius: 1rem; /* rounded-2xl */
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            padding: 40px;
        }
        .heading {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .quote {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-style: italic;
            color: #d1d5db; /* gray-300 */
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .footer {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #9ca3af; /* gray-400 */
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .quote::before,
        .quote::after {
            content: '"';
            color: #60a5fa; /* blue-400 */
            font-size: 2rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="heading">✨ Your Daily Inspiration ✨</div>
    <p class="quote">{{ quote }}</p>
    <div class="footer">
        Keep going with whatever you're doing, you'll get there!!<br> <br>
        Sent with ❤️ by Tom Emming
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
